re the amazons.  Hera had longed to help the amazons...but the look she feared in Hippolyte's eyes..kept her far away. <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 219<br> <font color=#993300>(1/24/01 8:14 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The hidden temple in the caves of the Black Sea</span><hr size=1> :::Hippolyte had packed up one of her horses for the journey to the coast of the Black Sea.  There was one place she had yet to check...that was close enough to travel...to find Hera.  She knew that Greece was too far away.  And would not be able to make that kind of treck, and return in time to prepare Themiscrya for the upcoming hard winter.  She urged the mare thru the forest trail that lead to the cave that very few new off.  A cave that held the ancient temple of Hera, from her days as the Goddess of the Underworld.  It was from a time, before Hera had become the wife of Zeus.  When she helped her brother, Hades rule the dead....long before she took the job as Goddess of Marriage and Childbirth.  Hera had shown this temple, to Hippolyte when she was rearing the child.  It had become their special place.  A place that they could get away from the troubles of Mt Olympus.  And just be "mother" and child.  Hippolyte smiled as she thought of those memories.  Then her breath released a soft sigh...and continued her journey:::  <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 224<br> <font color=#993300>(1/25/01 7:00 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The hidden temple in the caves of the Black Sea</span><hr size=1> :::Soon, Hippolyte was riding down the trail that lead to down to the beach.  The horse was carefull moving over the rocky path...and then jogged a bit freely as it found the soft sands.  Hipp gazed up the cliffs, her warm brown eyes searching for the cave and then stopped her mare as she found it.  She slid off the horse...and began the steep climb up to the mouth of the cave.  It had been a long time since she had done this, and forgot how sharp the rocks where to her hands.  Neverminding, she continued her climb::: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(1/26/01 4:01 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/QueenHera?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The hidden temple in the caves of the Black Sea</span><hr size=1> :::As Hera stood looking out to the sea...she suddenly sensed the familiar presence of Hippolyte, her granddaughter.  The Queen of the Gods walked to the edge of the cliff that jutted from the cave and looked down to see Hippolyte climbing up the long treacherous cliff.  Fearing her safety, Hera waved her hand and Hippolyte appeared before her.::: Hello, my daughter of the amazons.  :::Hera's pale ice blue eyes looked deeply into Hippolyte's own brown ones::: <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A> at: 1/26/01 4:03:07 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 226<br> <font color=#993300>(1/30/01 9:13 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The hidden temple in the caves of the Black Sea</span><hr size=1> :::Hipp suddenly found herself before Hera upon the cliff.  And then she smiled softly at Hera.  Then reached out with an extended arm and walked towards the Queen of the Gods.::: We do not hold this storm against you.  It is only Zeus's Order of Balance. :::she walks up and looks up slightly at the Goddess::Please, don't ever leave me like that again. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/01 11:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> never again</span><hr size=1> :::Hera smiled reassuring at Hippolyte's words and took her hand.  She wrapped her arms around the grown woman whom she had reared as if her own daughter.  Holding Hippolyte tenderly she kissed her on the forehead::: I am sorry, my little one.  I could not bear the look I feared from you. Because my actions would cause your tribe and you so much hardship. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 229<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/01 11:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Forgiven</span><hr size=1> :::She enjoyed the safe feeling in her grandmother's arms.  It reminded her of being a child on Olympus...and always knowing she could get out of trouble and be safe in those loving arms.  Brown eyes looked up at Hera::: I forgive you the punishment.  Nothing Zeus could do would turn my love from you, grandmother. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/01 11:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> forgiven</span><hr size=1> That means so very much to me, little one. :::Hera smiled down at Hippolyte.::: If there is anything I can do...tell me.  I will try and help you anyway I can.  I just cannot control Zeus's weather.  Tho, believe me I wish I could. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 230<br> <font color=#993300>(1/31/01 11:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Come with me</span><hr size=1> Then come with me, Grandmother.  We can use all the help we can receive.  And you know I love to have you around. ::she smiles::  It would be like old times...just ...colder. :::Hipp chuckles::: And we can handle anything old grumpy Zeus can dish out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#993300>(2/1/01 7:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Forgiven</span><hr size=1> I shall, my little one.  ::she smiles softly and brushes a wild strand of auburn hair from Hipp's cheek.:: I shall help Themiscrya survive this hard storm.  It is the least I could do for the amazons that I hold dear. ::: Suddenly with the wave of a delicate white hand...the Queen of the Gods and the Queen of Themiscrya dissappeared from the temple cave and appeared next to the altar in Hippolyte's hut.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showPrevMessage?topicID=141.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showNextMessage?topicID=141.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=141.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=141.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=141.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=141.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsunitefrm39">Guild Applications<option value="amazonsunitefrm61">Rules of